# Three-Tier Architecture

## 1. Presentation Layer (Frontend)

Technology:

* React.js
* Tailwind CSS
* React Router
* Axios

Responsibilities:

* User Interface
* Login & Registration
* Ride Booking
* Ride Tracking
* Driver Dashboard
* Admin Dashboard
* Payment Screen

---

## 2. Business Logic Layer (Backend)

Technology:

* Node.js
* Express.js

Responsibilities:

* Authentication
* Authorization
* Fare Calculation
* Ride Assignment
* Payment Processing
* Driver Matching
* Notification Service
* API Management

---

## 3. Data Layer

Technology:

* MongoDB
* Mongoose

Collections:

* Users
* Drivers
* Vehicles
* Rides
* Payments
* Ratings

