# Technology Stack Summary

| Layer          | Technology                    |
| -------------- | ----------------------------- |
| Frontend       | React.js, Tailwind CSS, Axios |
| Backend        | Node.js, Express.js           |
| Database       | MongoDB, Mongoose             |
| Authentication | JWT, bcrypt                   |
| Real-time      | Socket.IO                     |
| Maps           | Google Maps API               |
| Payments       | Razorpay / Stripe             |
| Image Storage  | Cloudinary                    |
| Deployment     | Vercel, Render, MongoDB Atlas |

This architecture is modular, scalable, and suitable for a production-style cab booking application. It separates concerns into presentation, business logic, and data layers, making the system easier to maintain and extend with features such as live tracking, notifications, and analytics.
